             A tribute to my Parents<br>
<br>
<br>
Everyday me and my parents would walk to the lake<br>
My parents knowing that their love was fate<br>
<br>
One day as while we were strolling back to town<br>
We heard the metal clashing, t'was a thunderous sound<br>
<br>
We ran to see what had gone so badly<br>
Only to find Romans killing our town sadly<br>
<br>
My Father fought back with all his might<br>
Only to fall and his last thing in sight <br>
<br>
was my mother being raped and murdered and me running away<br>
away from it all and as I ran I grew tired so I slept under a tree until day.<br>
<br>
When I awoke I found I was under the care<br>
of a woman named Mischa Teloska. one of those few to dare.<br>
<br>
She took me in as family just as her own<br>
She taught me how to stand on my own<br>
<br>
She died when I saw 27 I did mourn<br>
I was so sad and angry nearly torn<br>
<br>
I left her small village and carried on my way<br>
I never thought I'd make it until one day<br>
<br>
I met a Shamaness who taught me the ways of  warrior women<br>
Known as Amazons. I was excited that I was becoming one of them<br>
<br>
Yet again my closest friend died <br>
I told myself to go on and not to cry<br>
<br>
I have the title of Amazon Bard I have to give it honor<br>
and no I am not copying the blonde named Renee O' Connor<br>
<br>
I love my life and now I am rejoined by my friend Yakut she came back from the dead<br>
Now I ask Hippolyte to let me join her tribe. Now that all is done and said.<br>
<br>
(Sorry bout the Renee O'Conner part. I didnt know anything else to rhyme with honor)   <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=128.topic"> << Prev Topic </a> &nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=117.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=125.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=125.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.threadControl?topicID=125.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=125.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=125.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="amazonsuniteamazonsunitescrollboard">Amazons Unite Scroll Board<option value="amazonsunitefrm23">The Olympian Gods<option value="amazonsunitefrm15">Black Sea Tavern and Inn<option value="amazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya">Sist